{"type":"message","id":"93416fed","parentId":"66393780","timestamp":"2026-04-01T20:14:10.891Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's another session (a sub-agent) that was active about 22 minutes ago (updatedAt: 1775073112499, current time is 1775074429542, so about 22 minutes ago). This is within the 30-minute window but it's a sub-agent, not a user conversation. The sub-agent session appears to have completed its task (it says \"任务完成\" in its last message). \n\nThe cron job asks about \"活跃对话\" (active conversation) with user messages in the last 5 minutes. The sub-agent is not a user conversation - it's an agent doing background work. Let me check if there have been any recent user messages. The sub-agent session's last message was about 22 minutes ago, and the cron session just started now.\n\n\nSince the sub-agent represents completed background work rather than an active user dialogue, and the cron task itself has no user interaction, I should treat this as idle and proceed with self-learning. I'll read the miaoda-web-search skill to understand the proper approach for this.","thinkingSignature":"149dfff0c52b3e1b8d6f29541dad80531caeddd56270c5f82b5c395b2616eb4c"},{"type":"text","text":"有一个约22分钟前活跃的子Agent任务（已显示\"任务完成\"），不是用户对话。当前无活跃用户对话，执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rhsmvz2x34eu_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2412,"output":286,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46679,"cost":{"input":0.0007235999999999999,"output":0.0003432,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0023862299999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775074440551}}
{"type":"message","id":"2af83ad2","parentId":"93416fed","timestamp":"2026-04-01T20:14:10.899Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rhsmvz2x34eu_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775074450895}}
